intro: Become a star pilot and fly through the universe of quizzes!
description:
A fun true-or-false quiz about stars, planets, and the mysteries of space!

• Is the Sun large enough to fit one million Earths inside?
• Is a day on Venus longer than a year on Venus?
• Can you really not hear any sound in space?

Discover fascinating facts about the cosmos in a simple two-choice quiz!
Answer ○ or × and see how much of a true space explorer you are!
